Te rog. nu o răni.

669
01:03:11.925 --> 01:03:14.161
Nu o răni. te rog.

670
01:03:15.597 --> 01:03:16.830
Vino spre mine.

671
01:03:20.934 --> 01:03:22.469
- Nu.
