690
01:04:50.124 --> 01:04:51.291
Cine eşti tu?

691
01:04:54.962 --> 01:04:56.497
Cine eşti tu?

692
01:04:56.631 --> 01:04:58.666
Nu!

693
01:05:01.603 --> 01:05:02.903
Cine eşti tu?

